column3: What is the highest mountain in Italy?
column4: SELECT DISTINCT ?subjOfProp WHERE { ?subjOfProp <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#type> <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/Mountain> . ?subjOfProp <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/locatedInArea> <http://dbpedia.org/resource/ITALY> . ?subjOfProp <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/elevation> ?num . } ORDER BY DESC(?num) LIMIT 1
column5: PREFIX dbo: <http://dbpedia.org/ontology/> PREFIX res: <http://dbpedia.org/resource/> PREFIX rdf: <http://www.w3.org/1999/02/22-rdf-syntax-ns#> SELECT DISTINCT ?uri WHERE { ?uri rdf:type dbo:Mountain ; dbo:locatedInArea res:Italy ; dbo:elevation ?num } ORDER BY DESC(?num) OFFSET 0 LIMIT 1
